snippet.title: Long Story Teaser Masc Version
snippet.description:
LongStory Episode Two: Hanna's Locker follows the LongStory crew on their continued quest to discover the mystery of Locker 1224. Download the game at http://www.longstorygame.com/
Available February 12th, on IOS and Android.
